These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: go, billiard, canasta, backgammon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, october, march
4 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, turtle, rat
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 2. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
 3. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 5. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the bird and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 9. the owner of the rat is the person watching family movies##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
14. the person playing billiard is the owner of the turtle##1
15. the person playing billiard is not the person who's birthday is in april##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | go     | billiard   | backgammon | canasta |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Birthday         | april  | october  | march  | november |
| Pet     | mouse    | turtle | bird     | rat    |

