.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, davidoff, ritmeester
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, motorbike, quad-bike
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian, canadian, pakistani
 1. the person driving the motorbike is between the egyptian and the person driving the tram##2
 2. the old-henry-smoker is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the pakistani##8
 5. the egyptian is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
 7. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
 8. the canadian is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the bike is the brazilian##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
11. the egyptian is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
12. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
15. the swisher-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the brazilian##8
19. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Cigar      | swisher | davidoff | ritmeester  | old-henry  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Transport   | tram    | motorbike  | quad-bike | bike |
| Nationality           | canadian | pakistani | egyptian    | brazilian  |

