City: new-york, edinburgh, rome, san-francisco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar, dannemann, prince
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 5. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 7. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
12. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
