 3. the person eating plum is the owner of the fish##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the bird##2
 5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
13. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
15. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4

