 3. the person driving the train is not the cottage house##6
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
 7. the person driving the train is not to the left of the tower house##8
 8. the malaysian is the person who likes white##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
10. the person who likes green is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8
11. the person driving the trike is between the townhouse house and the person who likes white##2
12. the cottage house is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person who likes white##8
14. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3

.:: Answer ::.
