| Beverage           | iced-tea | fanta       | mirinda      | hot-chocolate  |
| Food   | asparagus    | banana | blueberry   | lime   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | r&b          | soul      | gospel  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | basketball      | rowing | lacrosse |

