 7. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the russian##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the american##7
11. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

